interpretation: The BACK arrow emoji signifies the need to go back and revisit a past decision, action or event. It can indicate a sense of regret or a desire to undo something that has been done. This card encourages reflection and introspection, urging you to consider whether a change of direction is necessary. It may also signify the return of someone or something from the past, or a desire to reconnect with old acquaintances. However, be cautious of getting stuck in the past and failing to move forward. Instead, use this card as an opportunity to learn from past mistakes and make better decisions going forward. Trust your instincts and have the courage to make the necessary changes in your life.
